PCI/ACPI: acpiphp: Rename alloc_acpiphp_hp_work() to alloc_acpi_hp_work()

Will need to use it for PCI root bridge hotplug support, so rename
*acpiphp* to *acpi* and move to osc.c.  Also make kacpi_hotplug_wq static
after that.

